<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Cookie" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
	<style>

	.emailpassword .container .passwordheader {
		text-align: center;
		font-family: cookie;
		background-color: black;
		color: white;
		border-bottom: 2px solid #C90832;
		font-size: 16px;
		height: 28px;
	}

	.emailpassword .container p {
		font-family: Times;
		font-size: 13px;
	}

	.emailpassword .container li {
		list-style: none;
		font-family: times;
		font-size: 13px;
	}

	.emailpassword .container a:link {
		text-decoration: none;
		color: #C90832;
	}

	.emailpassword .container a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<div class = "emailpassword">
		<div class = "container">
			<div class = "passwordheader"><h2>Footprint</h2></div>

			<p>Hi dear little stupid <%= @user.name %>, </p>
			<p>As your request, to reset your password click the link below:</p>
			<%= link_to "Reset password", edit_password_reset_url(@user.reset_token, email: @user.email) %>
			<p>Or, copy and paste in your browser: <%= edit_password_reset_url(@user.reset_token, email: @user.email) %></p>                       
			<p>Kind keep in mind that this link will expire in 2 hours.</p>

			<p>If you did not request your password to be reset, please ignore this email and your password will stay as it was.</p>

			<li>Love, </li>
			<li>Hu Xi</li>
			<li>Footprint, Co-founder</li>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
<html>